       Name: Hex Ward
       Kind: Skill
     Target: TAR_CHAR_OFFENSIVE
   Position: POS_FIGHTING
   Min Mana: 0
 Wait Beats: 24
 Can Learn: TRUE
Noun Damage: None
   Wear-Off: The hex ward eroding your defenses fades.
Acquisition:
   - Nightblade: level 10
Description:
   Hex Ward weaves shadow-compact entropy around the target, gradually
   eroding their defenses by worsening their AC for several rounds. This
   represents the Nightblade's "ward dissolution" doctrine -- applying hex
   effects that "progressively degrade spiritual protective wards before
   physical contact."

   Costs: Movement (via subtract_energy_cost)
   Cooldown: 20 rounds
   Duration: 3 + (Nightblade level / 5) rounds
   AC penalty to victim: +(Nightblade level * 4 + Warlock level * 2)

   Distinct from Dispel Magic (instant all-or-nothing buff removal). Hex
   Ward is gradual degradation that synergizes with the Nightblade's
   sustained-pressure doctrine, softening targets for precision strikes.
